Package: openmediavault-themekit
Architecture: all
Depends: openmediavault (>= 8.1.1), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Custom theme and accent color plugin for openmediavault
  A plugin that allows you to easily customize the openmediavault 8 web
  interface. It provides a system settings page to select a custom theme or accent color. Settings persist across openmediavault updates
  via an apt hook.
